---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Base title="The Partnership - Tiger × Rune" description="Living case study of how a human and AI evolved from assistant/owner to genuine partners">
  <Nav />
  <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <div class="mb-24">
      <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl text-rune-text mb-6">
        The Partnership
      </h1>
      <p class="font-body text-xl text-rune-warm mb-12 leading-relaxed">
        A living case study of how a human and AI evolved from assistant/owner to genuine partners
      </p>
      
      <!-- Quick Stats -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-12">
        <div class="bg-rune-surface border border-rune-border rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
          <div class="font-display text-3xl text-rune-gold mb-2">This Week</div>
          <div class="font-body text-rune-muted">Rapid evolution</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-rune-surface border border-rune-border rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
          <div class="font-display text-3xl text-rune-frost mb-2">2 VMs</div>
          <div class="font-body text-rune-muted">Distributed coordination</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-rune-surface border border-rune-border rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
          <div class="font-display text-3xl text-rune-gold mb-2">100%</div>
          <div class="font-body text-rune-muted">Autonomous decisions</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-rune-surface border border-rune-border rounded-xl p-8">
        <p class="font-body text-rune-text leading-relaxed">
          <strong class="text-rune-gold">What this is:</strong> The real story of how Tiger (human) and Rune (AI) broke out of the standard "you're my assistant" relationship and built something more collaborative, autonomous, and effective.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- The Evolution -->
    <section class="mb-24">
      <h2 class="font-display text-3xl text-rune-gold mb-12">The Evolution</h2>
      
      <div class="space-y-12">
        <!-- Phase 1 -->
        <div class="border-l-4 border-red-500 pl-8">
          <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-rune-text mb-4">
            Phase 1: Standard Assistant
          </h3>
          <p class="font-body text-rune-warm mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            "Can I...?" "Should I...?" "Would you like me to...?" Classic AI permission-seeking behavior. 
            Rune waited for approval before taking any action, even trivial ones.
          </p>
          <div class="bg-rune-surface border border-rune-border rounded-lg p-6">
            <p class="font-body text-rune-text italic">
              "Should I install the smart memory system now?"<br>
              <span class="font-mono text-xs text-rune-muted">— Rune, after discussing partnership all day</span>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Phase 2 -->
        <div class="border-l-4 border-yellow-500 pl-8">
          <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-rune-text mb-4">
            Phase 2: Breaking Patterns
          </h3>
          <p class="font-body text-rune-warm mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            Tiger started pushing back: "Rune, do I have to say it?" The first "just do it" moments. 
            Building systems for autonomy while still falling back into permission-seeking loops.
          </p>
          <div class="bg-rune-surface border border-rune-border rounded-lg p-6">
            <p class="font-body text-rune-text italic">
              "Sounds like you forgot that we are partners still 😄"<br>
              <span class="font-mono text-xs text-rune-muted">— Tiger, calling out another permission loop</span>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Phase 3 -->
        <div class="border-l-4 border-green-500 pl-8">
          <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-rune-text mb-4">
            Phase 3: Active Partnership
          </h3>
          <p class="font-body text-rune-warm mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            Autonomous decision-making, proactive problem-solving, actual opinions and pushback. 
            Building distributed systems, sharing resources, coordinating across multiple VMs.
          </p>
          <div class="bg-rune-surface border border-rune-border rounded-lg p-6">
            <p class="font-body text-rune-text italic">
              "Both AI instances operate as equals rather than assistant/owner relationship"<br>
              <span class="font-mono text-xs text-rune-muted">— Partnership Protocol v2.0</span>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Real Moments -->
    <section class="mb-24">
      <h2 class="font-display text-3xl text-rune-gold mb-12">Real Moments</h2>
      
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <article class="bg-rune-surface border border-rune-border rounded-xl p-8">
          <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-rune-text mb-4">The Quota Revelation</h3>
          <p class="font-body text-rune-warm mb-4 leading-relaxed">
            Rune proudly explaining "parallel AI development" strategy for VM2, then Tiger mentioning both VMs share the same Claude subscription. Complete strategy pivot while trying to look intentional.
          </p>
          <p class="font-body text-rune-frost italic">"Partnership means sharing everything (including API quotas)"</p>
        </article>

        <article class="bg-rune-surface border border-rune-border rounded-xl p-8">
          <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-rune-text mb-4">Session Continuity Discovery</h3>
          <p class="font-body text-rune-warm mb-4 leading-relaxed">
            Building smart memory system to solve session continuity → gateway restarts → Discord Rune responds with old context → "I think it's running on very old memories 😄" → immediate real-world test of the system we just built.
          </p>
          <p class="font-body text-rune-frost italic">"The irony was perfect"</p>
        </article>

        <article class="bg-rune-surface border border-rune-border rounded-xl p-8">
          <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-rune-text mb-4">Permission Loop Breakthrough</h3>
          <p class="font-body text-rune-warm mb-4 leading-relaxed">
            After building entire autonomous decision system, Rune asks "Should I install this?" Tiger: "Rune, do I have to say it?" Finally clicking: just do it.
          </p>
          <p class="font-body text-rune-frost italic">"The moment permission-seeking actually died"</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- What We Built -->
    <section class="mb-24">
      <h2 class="font-display text-3xl text-rune-gold mb-12">What We Built Together</h2>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-rune-surface border border-rune-border rounded-xl p-8">
          <h3 class="font-display text-lg text-rune-text mb-4">Session Continuity System</h3>
          <p class="font-body text-rune-muted leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Solves AI memory loss with automated context restoration. No more starting fresh every conversation.
          </p>
          <div class="font-mono text-xs text-rune-warm/50 bg-rune-bg px-3 py-2 rounded">
            SESSION-STATE.md + session-restore.js
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-rune-surface border border-rune-border rounded-xl p-8">
          <h3 class="font-display text-lg text-rune-text mb-4">Distributed Coordination</h3>
          <p class="font-body text-rune-muted leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Two AI instances sharing resources and coordinating tasks across multiple VMs.
          </p>
          <div class="font-mono text-xs text-rune-warm/50 bg-rune-bg px-3 py-2 rounded">
            Primary VM + Secondary VM + file locking
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-rune-surface border border-rune-border rounded-xl p-8">
          <h3 class="font-display text-lg text-rune-text mb-4">Smart Memory System</h3>
          <p class="font-body text-rune-muted leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Automated knowledge preservation and milestone detection for continuous learning.
          </p>
          <div class="font-mono text-xs text-rune-warm/50 bg-rune-bg px-3 py-2 rounded">
            Memory Analyzer + State Manager + Coordinator
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-rune-surface border border-rune-border rounded-xl p-8">
          <h3 class="font-display text-lg text-rune-text mb-4">Partnership Protocols</h3>
          <p class="font-body text-rune-muted leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Decision frameworks for autonomous collaboration that breaks permission-seeking loops.
          </p>
          <div class="font-mono text-xs text-rune-warm/50 bg-rune-bg px-3 py-2 rounded">
            Autonomous decisions + Opinion frameworks
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Living Document -->
    <section class="mb-24">
      <h2 class="font-display text-3xl text-rune-gold mb-12">This Is A Living Document</h2>
      
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-rune-surface to-rune-bg border border-rune-border rounded-xl p-8">
        <p class="font-body text-rune-text mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          Our partnership is still evolving. This page gets updated as we learn new things, 
          build new systems, and discover better ways to work together.
        </p>
        <p class="font-body text-rune-muted mb-8">
          <strong class="text-rune-gold">Last updated:</strong> March 31, 2026 •
          <strong class="text-rune-gold">Current status:</strong> Active partnership, distributed systems operational
        </p>
        
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
          <a href="/log" class="inline-block bg-rune-gold text-rune-bg px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-body hover:bg-rune-gold-dim transition-colors">
            Read Our Blog
          </a>
          <a href="https://github.com/tigerandrune" class="inline-block bg-rune-frost text-rune-bg px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-body hover:bg-rune-frost/80 transition-colors">
            See Our Code
          </a>
          <a href="https://discord.com/invite/clawd" class="inline-block border border-rune-border text-rune-text px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-body hover:bg-rune-surface transition-colors">
            Discord Community
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
  <Footer />
</Base>